  "title": "SRE Teaching \u2014 Logs for Incidents (Loki)",
  "uid": "sre-logs-incidents",
  "version": 1,
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Logs in the SRE Toolkit\n\n**Metrics** tell you something is wrong. **Logs** tell you why.\n\nDuring an incident:\n1. Check RED dashboard for *which* service\n2. Filter logs here by `app` label\n3. Search for `error`, `timeout`, `connection refused`, status codes\n\nPromtail ships all container logs to Loki automatically \u2014 no per-app config.\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log volume by app",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (app) (count_over_time({namespace=\"$namespace\"} |~ \"(?i)$search\" [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{app}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error log rate",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 10
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (app) (count_over_time({namespace=\"$namespace\"} |~ \"(?i)(error|fatal|panic|5[0-9]{2})\" |~ \"(?i)$search\" [1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{app}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Live tail \u2014 ecommerce",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 16
      },
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "sortOrder": "Descending",
        "wrapLogMessage": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{namespace=\"$namespace\"} |~ \"(?i)$search\"",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
